WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.720
conversation A. Hi John, how was your weekend?

00:05.720 --> 00:10.120
Great, I went fishing in the river near my house.

00:10.120 --> 00:12.480
Fishing? That sounds fun.

00:12.480 --> 00:19.680
Yes, you spend hours waiting and then suddenly there's a fish on your line. Then it's really

00:19.680 --> 00:27.720
exciting. Our family had a competition and my father caught the most. He caught seven

00:27.720 --> 00:29.680
fish in one day.

00:29.680 --> 00:32.440
Wow, that's great.

00:32.440 --> 00:36.640
But you know, my mother caught the biggest fish.

00:36.640 --> 00:38.520
And what about you?

00:38.520 --> 00:44.240
I only caught one, but Mum said it tasted the best of all.

